glycolysis nor enzyme kinetics

751
00:37:05.924 --> 00:37:08.058
will be covered
on tomorrow's midterm.

752
00:37:08.060 --> 00:37:09.760
- Yeah!
- Whoo-hoo!

753
00:37:09.762 --> 00:37:12.396
Okay. let's take
a five minute break.

754
00:37:12.398 --> 00:37:14.365
When we come back
we can do some review.

755
00:37:14.367 --> 00:37:17.168
I know a few of you wanted to
go back over protein folding.

756
00:37:17.170 --> 00:37:19.403
And you can ask
any other questions

757
00:37:19.405 --> 00:37:21.738
pertaining to the test.

758
00:37:42.193 --> 00:37:44.827
Uh. Andrew?

759
00:37:44.829 --> 00:37:46.862
Hey. I'm sorry.

760
00:37:46.864 --> 00:37:48.531
You caught me snacking.

761
00:37:49.734 --> 00:37:50.966
Cheddar pop chip?

762
00:37:50.968 --> 00:37:53.703
Oh. no.
No. thank you.

763
00:37:53.705 --> 00:37:57.239
Um. I was just wondering
if you could tell me. uh.

764
00:37:57.241 --> 00:37:59.742
what the last day
